\c 25
\nb
\v 1 Uba kukhona ukuxabana phakathi kwabantu, baye esahlulelweni, ukuthi babahlulele\x + 19.17.\x*, bazalungisisa olungileyo, balahle olecala\x + Zaga 17.15.\x*.
\v 2 Kuzakuthi-ke uba olecala efanele ukutshaywa, umahluleli uzamlalisa phansi, atshaywe phambi kwakhe, njengokulingene icala lakhe, ngokwenani.
\v 3 Angatshaywa \add imivimvinya\add* engamatshumi amane, angengezeleli, hlezi nxa esedlule ukumtshaya okwedlula le ngemivimvinya eminengi, kuze kuthi umfowenu ayangeke emehlweni akho\x + 2 Kor. 11.24.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Ungayifaki isayeke inkabi nxa ibhula\x + 1 Kor. 9.9. 1 Tim. 5.18.\x*.
\s Umlayo wokungena kumfazi ofelweyo
\p
\v 5 Uba izelamani zihlala ndawonye, lomunye wazo esifa, engelandodana, umfazi wofileyo kangendeli kowemzini ongaphandle; umfowabo wendoda yakhe uzangena kuye, amthathe abe ngumkakhe, enze kuye imfanelo yomfowabo wendoda\x + Mat. 22.24. Mark. 12.19. Luka 20.28.\x*.
\v 6 Kuzakuthi-ke izibulo alizalayo lizakuma ebizweni lomfowabo ofileyo\x + Gen. 38.9.\x*, ukuze ibizo lakhe lingacitshwa koIsrayeli\x + Ruthe 4.10.\x*.
\v 7 Uba umuntu engathandi ukuthatha umkamfowabo, umkamfowabo uzakwenyukela esangweni kubadala athi: Umfowabo wendoda yami uyala ukuvusela umfowabo ibizo koIsrayeli; kafuni ukwenza kimi imfanelo yomfowabo wendoda\x + Ruthe 4.1,2.\x*.
\v 8 Abadala bomuzi wakhe bazambiza-ke, bakhulume laye. Uba eqinisa esithi: Kangithandi ukumthatha\x + Ruthe 4.6.\x*;
\v 9 umkamfowabo uzasondela-ke kuye phambi kwamehlo abadala, akhuphe inyathela lakhe enyaweni lwakhe\x + Ruthe 4.7.\x*, amkhafulele ebusweni\x + Nani 12.14.\x*, aphendule, athi: Kuzakwenziwa njalo kulowomuntu ongayakhiyo indlu yomfowabo\x + Ruthe 4.11. Gen. 16.2. 30. 3.\x*.
\v 10 Lebizo lakhe lizakuthiwa koIsrayeli: Indlu yolenyathela elakhutshwayo.
\p
\v 11 Nxa amadoda esilwa, omunye lomunye, kusondele umfazi wenye ukuthi ayikhulule indoda yakhe esandleni soyitshayayo, elule isandla sakhe ayibambe ngamaphambili,
\v 12 usiqume isandla sakhe, ilihlo lakho lingabi lasihawu\x + 7.16.\x*.
\s Umthetho wezilinganiso
\p
\v 13 Ungabi lamatshe okulinganisa\x + Levi 19.36. Hez. 45.10.\x* ehlukeneyo esikhwameni sakho\x + Zaga 16.11. Mika 6.11.\x*, elikhulu lelincinyane.
\v 14 Ungabi lama-efa ehlukeneyo endlini yakho, esikhulu lesincinyane\x + Levi 19.36. Hez. 45.10.\x*.
\v 15 Woba lelitshe lokulinganisa elipheleleyo lelilungileyo, woba le-efa epheleleyo lelungileyo, ukuze insuku zakho zelulwe elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona\x + 4.40.\x*.
\v 16 Ngoba wonke owenza izinto ezinje, wonke owenza ukungalungi, uyisinengiso eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho\x + Zaga 11.1.\x*.
\s Icala lamaAmaleki
\p
\v 17 Khumbula lokho uAmaleki akwenza kuwe\x + Eks. 17.8.\x* endleleni ekuphumeni kwenu eGibhithe\x + 24.9.\x*,
\v 18 ukuthi wakuhlangabeza endleleni, watshaya phakathi kwakho ababebuthakathaka emva kwakho\x + Josh. 10.19.\x*, usudiniwe usuphele amandla; kanti kamesabanga uNkulunkulu\x + 2 Sam. 17.2.\x*.
\v 19 Ngakho kuzakuthi, nxa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho isikuphumuzile kuzo zonke izitha zakho inhlangothi zonke, elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona libe yilifa ukudla ilifa lalo\x + 1 Sam. 15.2,3.\x*, uzakwesula ukukhunjulwa kukaAmaleki ngaphansi kwamazulu; ungakhohlwa\x + Eks. 17.14.\x*.
